<h2>Samsung Galaxy Ring — Best for Android ($299)</h2>
<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576566588028-4147f3842f27?w=800&q=80" alt="Samsung Galaxy Ring analysis" style="width:100%;border-radius:10px;aspect-ratio:16/9;object-fit:cover;margin-bottom:20px;" loading="lazy"/>
<p>The Samsung Galaxy Ring is the best no-subscription option for Android users. Its Samsung Health integration is exceptional, sleep analysis is solid and automatic exercise detection beats most competitors.</p>
