<h2>Ultrahuman Ring Air — Best for iPhone ($249)</h2>
<p>For iPhone users who don't want a subscription, the Ultrahuman Ring Air is the best option. It's the lightest ring on the market (2.4g), its app is well designed and offers accurate sleep tracking with no monthly fee.</p>
